DESCRIPTION:Review first week of calibration reports and decide on Phase 2 auto-tuning.\n\nChecklist (docs/backend/calibration-report.md):\n- Review tuning_log table — suggestions from first 7 days\n- Were any CRITICAL flags triggered?\n- Bench ratio: is 25 docs/day still the right budget?\n- Entity yield: is ~19 entities/doc representative?\n- Orphan edge rate trend\n- Decide: enable Phase 2 auto-tuning for BUDGET parameter?\n- Feed audit: go-into-the-story and SC Film Commission\n\nCommands to run before meeting:\n  make calibration-report DOMAIN=film\n  sqlite3 data/db/film.db "SELECT * FROM tuning_log ORDER BY logged_at DESC LIMIT 20;"
